title: "AFX platform, lab 1, matched normal colon tissue, biological rep 1"
source_name_ch1: "Sample type N (Normal, matched normal colon tissue)"
extract_protocol_ch1: "Colorectal adenocarcinomas and matched normal colonic RNA sample were purchased from Oncomatrix, Inc., San Diego, CA."
label_protocol_ch1: "5 Âµg of total RNA was used to synthesize cRNA for each sample."
hyb_protocol: "20 Âµg of cRNA was hybridized to each individual microarray (HG-U133-Plus-2.0). The microarrays were hybridized for 16 hours at 45Â°C, stained, and washed according to an Affymetrix protocol (EukGE-WS2v4) using an Affymetrix fluidics station."
scan_protocol: "GeneChips were scanned using the Affymetrix scanner."
data_processing: "The CEL file data were analyzed with BioConductor to generate probeset level data using the justPlier() function. Probe-level data were quantile normalized before PLIER summarization per test site (10 arrays). An offset value of 16 was then added to each probeset-level data point."
